data.database_description: This database tracks information about students, including their personal details and academic activities such as major, advisor, and city code. It also records which video games they play and how much time they spend playing them, as well as their involvement in sports, detailing the sport name, hours per week spent, number of games played, and scholarship status. The relationships between tables are established through foreign keys linking students to both their gaming and sporting activities, providing a comprehensive view of each student's extracurricular interests and commitments.
